      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>I already tried talking to people and it doesn't help. It's like they say \"it'll get better\" because they don't want to deal with the reality of it. But the reality is that the person I actually want to talk to is gone. Everything just feels pointless now. Like I'm just going through the motions of a life that doesn't even belong to me anymore. It's just constant, exhausting pain.",
